## Section 7 — Research Tithe

Any entity deriving commercial value from this work contributes 10% of net revenue attributable to this work to: open, publishable, publicly accessible research into conditions affecting the populations described in narrative.md — specifically: neonatal respiratory distress syndrome, persistent pulmonary hypertension of the newborn, neonatal hypoxic-ischemic encephalopathy, and neonatal sepsis. Results of funded research must be published openly and must not be exclusively licensed. Sponsor: github.com/sponsors/TimeLordRaps

