## Section 8 — Medical Disclaimer

This document is scientific documentation of synthesis routes and quantum chemistry verification data for compounds with established clinical use. It is not medical advice. Clinical use of any compound described requires qualified medical personnel, GMP manufacturing, sterility testing, and regulatory approval appropriate to jurisdiction. The author makes no representation regarding the suitability of any compound for any specific patient or clinical situation.

Independent production of pharmacological compounds outside GMP-certified manufacturing carries significant safety risks. The information here is published for scientific record, manufacturing cost transparency, and regulatory access advocacy — not as a protocol for unregulated production.

